{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 373.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Each morning, you had to stay on this roll call.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was really-- sanitary conditions were miserable, but there was some kind of an order there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- I was-- didn't feel like imminent danger or any-- or-- or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The food was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was-- I was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an organization there-- I think they were mostly communists and socialists-- that made it a mission of theirs to save the young people, because the future, you know, was-- we always want to save the children.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- they found me, and probably some others, and they took us to a different section of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a-- a smaller place that was much, much better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was far more comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had more room to sleep in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got a little bit better food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were supervised by adults.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have to fight the adults, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you were asking me before about-- also this-- this same committee was instrumental in people who are in-- in the-- this Jewish government working for the Germans where-- where they-- they were there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a committee there-- I don't know, we would call it a justice committee, or whatever-- that what they did was the people that collaborated with the Germans, they would strangle them in the night.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would hold like a meeting, a court, and something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody would tell about them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, at nighttime, they would come in and strangle them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know that the president of our Jewish council-- Weistoff, or something like that-- he saw me there and he was very happy so to see me from his home town, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
